@page "/privacy"
@layout PublicLayout

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy - grow.IT</PageTitle>

<div class="contact-page footer-info-page">
    <section class="contact-hero">
        <span class="contact-kicker">Legal</span>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: February 27, 2026. This policy explains how grow.IT collects, uses, and protects personal and operational data.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-form-section">
        <article class="contact-form-card">
            <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect account information, organization setup details, service documentation data, and system telemetry needed to operate the platform and support your team.</p>

            <h2>How We Use Data</h2>
            <p>Data is used to deliver core product functionality, secure access, process reporting workflows, support troubleshooting, and improve platform quality.</p>

            <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>We do not sell personal data. We may share data with infrastructure and service providers strictly for hosting, support, communications, and security operations.</p>

            <h2>Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain data for as long as needed to provide services, meet contractual obligations, and satisfy legal or compliance requirements.</p>

            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You may request access, correction, export, or deletion of eligible data by contacting our team through the contact page.</p>
        </article>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-cta">
        <div class="contact-cta-card">
            <h2>Questions about privacy handling?</h2>
            <p>Contact our team for clarification on data processing and retention practices.</p>
            <div class="contact-cta-actions">
                <a href="/contact?subject=Privacy%20Question" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
                <a href="/security" class="btn btn-outline">View Security</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
